description:
Talented but aimless Sakurai just can't find a place to belong. After trying (and failing at) one extracurricular activity after another, his life changes thanks to a chance encounter with lacrosse fanatic Toyoguchi, who thinks Sakurai has just what it takes to propel her girls' lacrosse team to victory!

Now that Sakurai is the manager of the girls' lacrosse team, his number one priority is readying his struggling players for the upcoming spring tournament. It's bad enough that his tough practices drive players to quit, but to make matters worse, when a talented rival aims for Misora's affections, he loses his cool. Can Sakurai really handle his new position?

  • Chapter 12: Three-Day Weekend

name: Together

description:
Talented but aimless Sakurai just can't find a place to belong. After trying (and failing) one extracurricular activity after another, his life changes thanks to a chance encounter with lacrosse fanatic Toyoguchi, who thinks Sakurai has just what it takes to propel her girls lacross team to victory!

After tons of hard work, sweat, and tears, the team enters their first tournament. But if they want to be challengers, they'll have to up their fame both on and off the field-not only does goalie Komatsu need one-on-one top training, but she and the team's top players need to bring their grades up. And if they do advance, they'll have to face the league's toughest team-Choran.

name: Until I Met You

description:
Can a lacrosse team be saved by a spear and shield? Sakurai thinks so, and stakes Fujioka’s chances in the game against the unbeatable Choran on Operation: Spear and Shield. The strategy relies on forging a defense as impenetrable as a shield and puncturing Choran’s ironclad defense with an unheard of long-distance pass. There’s very little time to practice, and Choran has a few tricks up its sleeve too. The game begins!

Chapter Titles

  • Chapter 27: Two More Days
  • Chapter 28: Thoughts Before the Final Tournament
  • Chapter 29: Justice Will Prevail

description:
An adventure that plunges us into the source of the Order of the Dragon Knights

As they are about to be slaughtered by a Dragon, two Knights are saved when villagers intervene, who, by helping them, obey ancient prophecies. A huge statue is then discovered; that of the “Goddess”, a female matriarchal and powerful divinity. In a world where Hâman priests are the law, temptation is great for the Order of the Dragon Knights to support the Goddess and impose a new power…
name: La Déesse

description:
IN ARSALAM, THE WAR AGAINST THE SARDES RAGES !

There are thousands of them… Sardes, tribes, warriors, barbarians, coming down on the Empire. Surrounded by enemies of the court, the Empress is alone.

In the little town of Arsalam, on the border of the western roads and the Closed Sea, the Dragon Knights hold… They have been resisting, for years, they keep resisting, again and always, against savage hordes, without backup, without supplies. Their enemies are no longer the Dragons but the humans…
name: La Guerre des Sardes - Partie 1

description:
CRISSE'S FIERY HEROIN IS FINALLY BACK !

Atalante and the Argonauts, having gotten the winged horses back, go to free the Boreads from the harpies’ claws. Atalante, although concentrating on the battles, relives the wounds of her past over and over again…
name: Calaïs et Zétès

description:
MORE OF THE EPIC ATALANTE SAGA !

Atalante and her companions weren’t able to free the Boreades from the harpies’ claws. Despite their sadness and exhaustion they continue their quest for the gold fleece…

But the ocean isn’t on their side: shipwrecked on an unknown beach, they find themselves facing mysterious specters! A dangerous encounter that will take them to the kingdom of Hades!
name: Le Labyrinthe d'Hadès

description:
AN ADAPTATION OF FRANCES HODGSON BURNETT’S NOVEL ‘A LITTLE PRINCESS’.

What little girl doesn’t know the tale of Princess Sara, an orphan at a horrific boarding school...diamond mines... the London fog...? Soleil have made their very own steampunk adaptation of the novel that inspired the famous manga of the 80s.
name: Pour une mine de diamants

description:
ANOTHER KIND OF LIFE BEGINS FOR SARA…

Terrible news: her father is dead and didn’t leave her a penny. From that moment on the little princess finds herself reduced to being a servant. In the very boarding school where her fortune was admired by all, Sara must now follow the orders of her former classmates. The servants, as for them, are happy to get their revenge… She will pay for all the tantrums of these golden youths.
name: La princesse déchue

description:

description:
MORE ADVENTURES FOR THE ORPHAN PRINCESS, IMAGINED BY ALWETT.

The years have gone by since Sara Crewe got her fortune back. But she will only find peace when she gets back the machine factory belonging to her family. But the new owner has no desire to sell it. Sara doesn’t get discouraged and comes back to the Indies with a fake identity…
name: Retour aux Indes

volume.name: Zero: The Beginning of the Coffin

description:
JENNA AND JIM DOUBLE ACT! THIS TIME, THEY’RE UP AGAINST ONE OF THE CITY’S MOST POWERFUL GODFATHERS…

Although they succeeded in solving their last case, Jim and Jenna have ended up in jail. Awaiting judgement, the former special agents employ their time usefully to plan their revenge…
name: L'affaire du détenu 3491

description:
THE SO DESERVED REST OF JENNA AND JIM WILL BE SHORT-LIVED…

Jim Mc Kalan is one of the top assets in the King’s Secret Service. His cousin Jenna provides him with vital help in each of his investigations. Between murders and disappearances, they thwart the most Machiavellian plans ! One question remains about them ; they have never been seen together except once…What is their secret ?
name: L'affaire Rivendalwn

description:
A NEW ADVENTURE FOR OUR DYNAMIC INVESTIGATORS!

In a county close to York City, Trinski army commander in chief, foments a coup and takes power. For the Royal Office it is vital to overturn this dictatorship that could plunge the entire area into a civil war. Jim and Jenna Mc Kalan are in charge of helping the resistance. It’s the beginning of a highly dangerous mission, the outcome of which will have effects on the whole country…
name: L'affaire Trinski

description:
A NEW GRIPPING INVESTIGATION FOR ONE OF THE JEWELS OF STEAMPUNK COMIC BOOKS!

9 am. Three simultaneous explosions go off... The tram on line 17B Ompton Cross was just pulverized, just like the hellion of flight 710 to Velko and the commuter train to New York city. The toll is high: 135 dead and about 50 wounded. Now starts a man hunt where each second counts to avoid a new attack... What Jim, Jenna and their collaborators still ignore, is that they are directly threatened...
name: L'affaire mentaliste

description:
A new investigation filled with suspense for Jim and Jenna!

Marnie will finally say yes to her fiancé! Therefore in front of dozens of witnesses… Marnie is slaughtered by Beltran, one of the Royal Office’s greatest enemies. Within a few minutes, Jim and Jenna will have to get organized to go against the diabolical plans of this invader who is well decided to take over all powers!
name: L'affaire Marnie

description:
WHAT HAPPENS WHEN YOU FIND THE STORY OF YOUR OWN LIFE IN AN ANCIENT AND MYSTERIOUS VOLUME …?

Roman Guénodon, a young boy from a well-to-do family, finds it hard to sparkle in high society, much to his father’s chagrin. His only means of escape from this world is to immerse himself in his books…But one day, a man gives him The Book of Destiny, a mysterious work that reveals to its readers their own destinies … So Roman plunges into the incredible adventure that is beckoning!
name: Le Premier Pas

description:
BY THE CREATOR OF «LA QUÊTE DE L’OISEAU DU TEMPS».

A young man from a wealthy family, Roman Guénodon cannot manage, however, to shine in society, to the regret of his father. His only release from a world he does not understand is to dive into adventure novels and enjoy the trials and tribulations of their heroes … But what would happen if Roman discovered the story of his own life written down, black on white, in a mysterious, ancient work… Trap or freedom ?
name: Silverman

description:
WELCOME TO THE DARK ENCHANTMENT OF ANCESTRAL BRITTANY!

They are three fairy queens, three morgan sisters. Each one inherited a part of the legendary Triskell that symbolizes the forces of Brittany: Sea, Wind and Earth. Gwen is a young orphan entrusted with the Wind part and immediately finds herself confronted with the harsh world of fairies.
name: La marque de l'Entre-Monde

description:
THE TRISKELL SAGA DRAWS TO AN END

They are three fairy queens, three morgan sisters. Each one inherited a part of the legendary Triskell that symbolizes the forces of Brittany: Sea, Wind and Earth. Gwen is a young orphan entrusted with the Wind part and immediately finds herself

confronted with the harsh world of fairies.
name: Guerre et Fées

description:
The new offbeat series by Arleston and Barbucci!

When Fourmille gets on her plane for New York, she is far from imagining that her journey will take a strange direction. In the middle of the flight, she is accosted by a strange creature who asks her is she accepts the inheritance of an aunt who disappeared 20 years ago. And after lightning strikes the 747, it is on a dragon’s back that she lands in New York. Deep in a Manhattan heroic fantasy, she then discovers a completely offbeat world.
name: New York

description:
AFTER NEW YORK, DISCOVER ARLESTON AND BARBUCCI'S VERSION OF PARISIAN HEROIC FANTASY !

Fourmille Gratule now lives in New York, in the world of Ekhö, a mirror world of the Earth where modern technology doesn’t exist.

At the head of the artistic agency Gratule, inherited from her aunt Odelalie, she goes to Paris for a new contract. She barely gets to the French capital before her body is taken over by the ghost of Prince Antone, Napoleon VII’s son who died in a carriage accident. She will have to solve the mystery of his death to become her old self again…
name: Paris Empire

description:
IRRESISTIBLY DRAWN TO ONE ANOTHER, THE FIVE CHILDREN OF THE PROPHECY HAVE FINALLY FOUND EACH OTHER.

From their union the power of Kookaburra has burst forth, sweeping away the entire universe. A cycle has come to a close… Could anyone have escaped it? No-one... except the possessor of the ‘Golden Pearl’ containing the secrets of Life: Dragan Preko! Disenchanted, he is constantly haunted by the same apocalyptic nightmare… Until the night he realises that something has just changed…But is Dragan really the only one to have survived the cataclysm?
name: L'héritier des âmes

description:
A NEW CHAPTER RICH IN REVELATIONS FROM THE FABULOUS SPACE OPERA!

Dragan Preko is the only survivor of the annihilation of his universe during the mortal combat between the two powerful divinities. Thanks to the golden pearl hidden in the bottom of his eye, he survived everything and has been there for 10 000 years! The pearl’s power made him immortal. Of this pearl, as of his past, he knows nothing. But for an unknown reason, the veil is finally lifted on his memories and his fears…
name: La perle d'or
